Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.14,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Meus tímpanos não vão aguentar-nen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.05,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.13,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Isso é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.70,Pensante,,0,0,0,,A Caixa Tamate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.42,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.84,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:22.18,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Quem está incomodando\N o Gastino-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.69,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Irmão mais velho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.79,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ele vai me matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.36,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Irmão mais velho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.41,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.14,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.14,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar vocês irem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.84,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Cubram-nos-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.82,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Rápido-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.99,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.86,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vou espremer você até a morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.07,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.36,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.78,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nós seremos seus oponentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.51,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.26,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Q-Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.45,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Queima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.46,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Não vão escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.08,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Chormano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.12,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Gênio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:23.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Germa 66!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desgraçados!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Morram queimados!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Esse é...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:16.62,Pensante,,0,0,0,,A tecnologia da Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:19.94,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Essas são as armaduras \Nque lembram sua forma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.72,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Resistem ao fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.85,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vou endurecê-las com\N meu doce de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Candy Wave!
