Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.44,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\clip(0,0,1279,719)\move(58,72,58,-50,2480,2980)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.44,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\clip(0,0,1279,719)\move(58,72,58,-50,2480,2980)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.44,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2480,2980)}Relâmpago azul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:22.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não é grande coisa,\N mesmo com um corpo tão enorme.
