Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.73,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.20,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Estão bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.36,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.39,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.77,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz que você esteja bem, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Jet Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.60,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.60,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.04,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.45,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.72,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nós também estamos recuando-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.81,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ora, ora, a Caixa Tamate, \No tesouro lendário!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:56.72,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Aqui ninguém vai me encontrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.78,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Que caótico-nen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:03.55,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vou aproveitar para trocar\N o que tem dentro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:46.12,Pensante,,0,0,0,,É nossa última chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.21,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Disparo do Canhão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.14,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Maldição!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.58,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Parede de Doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.84,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Perospero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.66,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ah, isso doeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.31,Pensante,,0,0,0,,A Germa se juntou a eles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:12.38,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se, desgraçados!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.85,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Você não vai rir para sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.26,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.86,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.29,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.29,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\clip(0,0,1279,719)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.29,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\clip(0,0,1279,719)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.29,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\clip(0,0,1279,719)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.29,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Em marcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:48.05,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vou atirar nas costas dela\N até que as balas acabem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.70,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Morra, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:53.43,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Canhão...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.10,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...Disparo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.41,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,145)}O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:05.51,Pensante,,0,0,0,,{\fad(136,0)}Pai, eles destruíram os \Ncanhões da esquerda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:09.07,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Todos os canhões estão cheios de mochi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.25,Pensante,,0,0,0,,por isso não podemos atirar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:18.02,Pensante,,0,0,0,,K-Katakuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:22.49,OPLetreros,,0,0,26,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,705)}DENTRO DO BIG FATHER {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:26.02,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Um informe a todos no castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:44.82,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Os pés do Big Father foram \Nendurecidos com doce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.78,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Não podemos nos mover!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:55.65,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Seremos cercados pelos\N Piratas da Big Mom, a Yonkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:13:00.99,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,e teremos que lutar uma batalha sob cerco, da qual não temos esperança alguma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.78,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Eliminaremos quem quer que saia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.66,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Saiam já!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:33.19,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Te usaram uma e outra vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.86,Pensante,,0,0,0,,S-Sou a vítima, irmão mais velho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:39.10,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Chute a bunda de todos eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.10,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Veneno?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.10,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Que mulher irritante...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:04.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Apareceu, apareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é incrível, Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você se transformou neste\N castelo gigante!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Shiro Shiro no Mi é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há tempo para\N se alegrar com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Considerem a situação \Nem que estamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldita seja...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:20.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O plano de assassinato no qual trabalhamos por mais de um ano acabou em fracasso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que\N não consigo eliminar alguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:30.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No final das contas, os Yonkou\N estão em outro nível, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, o que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:35.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não temos nem um \Núnico minuto a perder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou lhes dizer por quê.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:39.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Escutem com atenção!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este castelo sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é forte, mas não invencível.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:46.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se destruírem o castelo, eu morro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O castelo desaparecerá...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:52.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E uma vez que estiverem fora, \Nserão comida daqueles monstros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Comida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.34,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Comida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou perdoar vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:14.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Posso sentir a raiva da\N mama por todo o meu corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:35.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão viver um inferno, tanto se saírem\N quanto se ficarem aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Compreendam que estamos em apuros!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me culpe, Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aquele míssil era o mais \Navançado do mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querido, você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É lá fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá fora?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam daí!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela está nos olhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:31.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom recuperou a consciência!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam todos do castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mostrem a cara, idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você me traiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:58.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,460)}Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Resista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que medo, que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.84,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Que medo, que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saia, Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuide do Pez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama, sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege é meu marido\N e temos um filho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Perdoe-o, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Faça vista grossa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:43.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você sempre parece idêntica à Lola...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1108,702)}Lá vem ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(176,702)}Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Recue, Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.65,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:55.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já disse para não me\N mostrar esse rosto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.17,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:11.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você também é cúmplice, Chiffon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:14.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pense que poderá\N comer doces amanhã!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:15.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:24.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando o castelo for destruído e\N Bege estiver morto, todos sairão!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não deixem ninguém escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Piratas Firetank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéu de Palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:31.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E também Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Germa 66!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Arruinaram o casamento e a festa do chá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nos subestimaram demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos enforcá-los como exemplo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:51.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldita velha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:06.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Big Father nem se abala com \Nos disparos de canhão,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas contra ela não é páreo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:12.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou sair para chutar o traseiro dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chopper, pare ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, me solte!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me solte!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não responda aos ataques dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:32.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viemos para resgatar \No Sanji-kun, não foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos uma cópia do Poneglyph...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:39.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e até realizamos o desejo\N do Sanji-kun de salvar sua família!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já alcançamos nossos objetivos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:47.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você tem tempo para contra-atacar, \Nmelhor usar para pensar em como escapar daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:52.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se quiséssemos lutar, teríamos trazido o Zoro e os outros, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san, a Nami-san está certa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:59.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos nos infiltrar \Nporque somos poucos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos todos para o País de Wano, onde \No Zoro-san e os outros estão nos esperando!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:16.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, o que fazemos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:22.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Bege está levando\N os golpes por nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldita seja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossos resultados foram péssimos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:39.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acho justo que\N só vocês tenham sucesso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:42.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere um pouco, Bege-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:44.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não tente nos arrastar com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:46.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu fiz minha parte!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:49.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devolva meu coração!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:52.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Arrastar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é uma má ideia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:59.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desde o início, vocês \Nnunca me importaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:16.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...meus adoráveis subordinados...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e minha amada esposa e filho estão aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:25.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não posso deixar que morram!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Querido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.93,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só há uma maneira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de todos sobreviverem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:47.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só uma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Qual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:55.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:58.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou destruí-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:03.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele não vai aguentar muito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:06.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se para atacar \Na qualquer momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:09.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou esmagá-los com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos eliminar...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...até o último deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:18.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam já!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou prender vocês em um espelho!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:27.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A única forma de sobreviver...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...é...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:32.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...que este quarto\N dentro do Big Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,ou seja, o que está dentro de mim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:37.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.73,0:22:39.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se assustem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:44.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não importa o quão forte nos ataquem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.65,0:22:49.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ou se o Big Father se inclinar ou rolar...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:53.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só eu vou me machucar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:58.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto estiverem aqui, \Nnão serão afetados!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:22:59.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Certamente, Bege-san \Né o único que sofre.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:07.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ouvimos a voz da Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:12.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas aqui está tudo tranquilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:22.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E será o mesmo se eu voltar \Nà minha forma humana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Escutem...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:27.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou voltar à minha forma humana \Nenquanto vocês estão dentro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:32.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, o Caesar vai me carregar \Ne fugiremos voando.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:35.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se der certo, sairemos \Ndessa enrascada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:38.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:41.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você decide quando colocar\N minha vida em perigo, idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:44.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é suicídio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:47.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nesse momento, \Nvão nos surrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:49.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há nenhuma \Nchance de sucesso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:51.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Também há muitos usuários\N de Busoshoku Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.74,0:23:54.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não adianta se eu virar gás!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Responda o seguinte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:23:59.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:04.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você nos salvou?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:11.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,As pessoas que você mais odeia\Ncaíram completamente na armadilha dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:18.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Porque entristeceria meu pai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:24.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...que eu continuasse preso \Naos meus ressentimentos infantis...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.55,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Me libertem, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.55,0:24:29.89,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.89,0:24:31.39,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.57,0:24:36.49,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sinto ter nascido fraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.49,0:24:39.12,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Me ajude, pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.12,0:24:43.54,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,946)}Me ajude, pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:49.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele ficaria decepcionado se visse que eu\N me tornei um homem pequeno...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:53.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...capaz de rir da morte\N de sua própria família biológica.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:58.14,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(651,603)}Cuide-se dos resfriados.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.14,0:25:02.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero viver de uma forma\N que não possa...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.16,0:25:03.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...olhá-lo nos olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:12.39,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Nunca ouse dizer a ninguém...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.39,0:25:17.02,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...que eu sou seu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.90,0:25:25.11,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É uma desgraça que\N não quero que ninguém saiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.09,0:25:27.77,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você entende, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.21,0:25:33.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há treze anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.11,0:25:38.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Vinsmoke Sanji escapou\N da Germa e morreu no mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.55,0:25:41.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é o que você queria.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:55.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então admita...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.40,0:26:01.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...que você não é meu pai, \NVinsmoke Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:04.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não apareça mais diante de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.05,0:26:30.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.67,0:26:33.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prometo...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:35.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...que não me aproximarei de você...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.27,0:26:38.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...nem do East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.35,0:26:48.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já cumpri minha missão!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.17,0:26:50.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não faz parte do acordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:55.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não fizermos algo, \Nvocê também morrerá, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.83,0:26:58.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Abra a porta!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.75,0:27:02.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gang Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:05.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até que você e o Caesar\N Clown escapem voando,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.45,0:27:08.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,nós, da Germa,\N vamos escoltá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.02,0:27:09.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Espere um momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.37,0:27:12.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você decide\N o que eu vou fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:15.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você continua tão arrogante \Ncomo sempre, Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.35,0:27:19.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.69,0:27:22.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Germa também pode voar, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.04,0:27:24.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então vamos deixá-los para trás.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.24,0:27:25.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.86,0:27:30.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, se precisamos ganhar \Ntempo, eu também...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.92,0:27:33.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.42,0:27:34.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.59,0:28:00.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não quero dever\N nada a um fracasso!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.15,0:28:05.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É assim que eles acertam as contas.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.26,0:28:09.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem, esperem, ouçam, ouçam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.32,0:28:12.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não disse que faria isso, idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.70,0:28:14.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.34,0:28:16.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca e faça!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.31,0:28:18.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:21.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão me pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.42,0:28:27.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam já!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.65,0:28:29.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.27,0:28:39.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Germa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.50,0:28:41.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ao ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.50,0:28:41.43,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\NHalee,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e acene-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...bem no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços imutáveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos isso há muito tempo.
